rComments: She's more than willing to help when asked. She's very nice and tries her best to make herself clear. However, her lectures are often long and confusing a lot of times. Her midterms and finals are quite easy but they are very very long.
Excellent professor, wonderful at explaining concepts and very fair tests - what you see in class is what you get. A little quiet but if you can pay attention in class, you will get a high grade.
